<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Start</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select a date and a time when the live shopping offer should start.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>End</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select a date and a time when the live shopping offer should end.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Item ID</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Enter the item’s ID.<br>
<strong><em>Note:</em></strong> The same item cannot be offered in more than one live shopping offer during the same period.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Quantity sold</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Setting changes the displayed percentage of items that have been purchased in live shopping already.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Total</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Enter maximum quantity that can be sold at the discounted price. Regardless of this entry, there must be enough stock available for those items that are tied to the stock.<br>
If a customer tries to put a larger quantity into their shopping cart, then the quantity will automatically be reduced. As soon as this quantity has been sold, the item will be offered at the normal price again.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
