</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="_configuring_a_live_shopping_offer">2. Configuring a live shopping offer</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Configure newly created live shopping offers as described below.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Configuring a live shopping offer:</p>
</div>
