<h2 id="_publishing_live_shopping_offers">4. Publishing live shopping offers</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Live shopping offers can also be presented on external platforms such as the German site <a href="http://www.liveshopping-aktuell.de" target="_blank" rel="noopener">liveshopping-aktuell.de</a>. Register with the provider and save the offer’s URL as follows:</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p>Offer 1: your_domain/plenty/api/liveshopping_xml_1.php</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Offer 2: your_domain/plenty/api/liveshopping_xml_2.php</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>In these examples, the items for the first and second live shopping offer are exported.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Use the ID to specify which live shopping offer should be exported. Use the parameter <strong>SHIPPING</strong> to set specific shipping costs.</p>
</div>
<div class="admonitionblock tip">
<table>
<tbody><tr>
<td class="icon">
<i class="fa icon-tip" title="Tip"></i>
